      "id": "PopularPost268736",
      "post_content": "I prefer this card over pillar of flame because it is an instant. Being an instant, it gives you more options and lets you use it during an opponents turn, comboing with creatures like Wee Dragonouts and Kiln Fiend to takedown bigger creatures if needed. It's also a great response to a turn 3 Geralf's Messenger, or Tuk Tuk, the explorer. ",
